metadata.name: StatusPin validations allows pins above the max for remote accounts

sql_query.sql: SELECT 1 AS one FROM "accounts" WHERE LOWER("accounts"."username") = 'bob' AND LOWER("accounts"."domain") = 'remote.test' LIMIT $1
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "instances" WHERE "instances"."domain" = $1 LIMIT $2
SELECT 1 AS one FROM "statuses" WHERE "statuses"."uri" = $1 LIMIT $2
